              "id": "QUE58395",
              "question": "Amelia has recently given birth to her first child. She mentions that she often goes into her babyâ€™s bedroom to check if he is still breathing. Would this qualify as an obsessive-compulsive disorder (OCD)?\n\u003cbr /\u003e",
